## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all nuances of the educational systems in China and the U.S. The findings are limited to the perspectives and data presented in the selected sources. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of educational policies and practices means that some information may become outdated quickly. Further research, including interviews with educators and students from both countries, could provide deeper insights.

